{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-06-12-1",
 "title": "Fixing the Wookiee's Lotto Machine",
 "summary": "In Nebula Plaza in Coronet City, the disguised agent Bazil McKenzie (as Mege Vauki) comes upon the battle-scarred old Wookiee Chongatakiee, who is furiously beating and shaking a malfunctioning lottery machine that swallowed his credits. Bazil offers to help, opens the terminal, and finds a loose power connection, repairing it and coaxing out the ticket Chonga wanted while gently joking about the Wookiee's stormtrooper-like assault on the machine. The two exchange names and warm respect, Bazil admiring the Wookiee people's heroism and Chonga -- who works as a technician for the Alliance -- offering his help should Bazil ever need it. They part with friendly farewells and a shared sense they may meet again.",
